did.abstract: The records consist of correspondence, meeting minutes, and reports of the Development and Alumni Affairs office documenting services and support for Yale School of Nursing alumni.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 29-E (YRG 29-E), Records of departments, offices, programs, and projects of the Yale School of Nursing.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: The materials were transferred from Development and Alumni Affairs, Yale School of Nursing, 2007.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the materials is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Development and Alumni Affairs, School of Nursing, Yale University, Records (RU 1029). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by topic, thereunder chronologically.

bioghist.head: Biographical / Historical
bioghist.p: The Yale School of Nursing Development and Alumni Affairs office is responsible for alumni relations and fundraising, and serves as liaison to the Alumnae/i Association.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of correspondence, meeting minutes, and reports of the Development and Alumni Affairs office documenting services and support for Yale School of Nursing alumni.
